OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome brightness to start then rain
OL,7,Fspreading north during the evening.
OL,8,FThis clearing shortly after midnight
OL,9,Fto leave a dry night with some clear
OL,10,Fspells developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FWarm again on Friday. Dry
OL,13,Fthrough much of the day with bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells. The odd shower possible
OL,15,Fin the afternoon ahead of some rain in
OL,16,Fthe evening.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWarm
OL,19,Fover the weekend and on Monday with
OL,20,Fsome bright or sunny spells, chance of
OL,21,Fsome rain later on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
